MStruct++ - is a free computer program for MicroStructure analysis from powder diffraction data.

It is based on the free library ObjCryst++ (ref: http://vincefn.net/Fox/). The library is extended
by classes/routines for microstructural effects modelling.

MStruct++ is still under development. The authors apologize for lack of documentation.

Please, use this program with patience. You can contact the authors for help.

Contact:

